snippet.title: Paint the Town Red (Early Access Teaser)
snippet.description:
The first teaser of the upcoming Early Access release of Paint the Town Red on Steam. Coming October 2015.

Paint the Town Red on Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/337320 (Follow and add to Wishlist to be notified of release asap)

Music: Beethoven's "Egmont Overture"
